thread.title_full: Disc Makers reviewed by Timothy McCoy

author: Timothy McCoy
title: Timothy McCoy
text:
Disc makers made the CD I wanted to produce. I did not have to settle for something less than . They exceeded my expectations and were more than willing to make changes, however minor, until I was completely satisfied.
And I am completely satisfied, as are all of my fans!
